soot.jimple.spark.geom.ptinsE

Class PtInsIntervalManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • soot.jimple.spark.geom.geomPA.IFigureManager
      • soot.jimple.spark.geom.ptinsE.PtInsIntervalManager

  • public class PtInsIntervalManager
extends IFigureManager
    The figure manager for the PtIns descriptors. The implementation is almost same to the HeapIns manager, please refer to HeapInsIntervalManager for more detailed comments.
